employee-registration application uses to give a form to enter the employee details like name, address, email, password, telephone, designation, comment which will be saved to mongodb data base.
Once the details are entered we are able to edit the employee details and we are allowed to delete the details of individual employees also
Note: Here comments filed is optional


Tools Used:

1.Node.js(download it from https://nodejs.org/en/)
2.Mongodb(download if from https://www.mongodb.com/download-center?jmp=nav)
Note:  To download Mongodb u need to signup with u r persoanl email id
3.Pug(Install using npm install pug --save)
4.Javascript
5.Express.js(Install using npm install express --save)
6.MVC Framework


Refereces:

1.https://www.tutorialspoint.com/nodejs/
2.https://www.tutorialspoint.com/mongodb/
3.https://www.tutorialspoint.com/expressjs/
